    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick, with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Add the <strong>diced sweet potato</strong> to the pan and cook for 5 min for until lightly browned</p><p>Once lightly browned, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1720444206807-x200.jpg",
