    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>paneer</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped paneer</strong> and <strong>courgette discs</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>remaining curry powder</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is you <strong>marinated paneer</strong> <strong>& courgette</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
