    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat the grill to medium-high</p><p>Thread the <strong>marinated paneer</strong> <strong>& courgette</strong> onto the <strong>soaked skewers</strong> and add them to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the tray under the grill for 8-12 min, turning once halfway, or until slightly charred – these are your <strong>mango paneer & courgette skewers</strong></p>",
