    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and chop finely</p><p>Once the paneer skewers are almost ready, return the <strong>basmati</strong> <strong>rice</strong> to a low heat then add the <strong>chopped spinach </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and cook for 1 min or until the spinach has slightly wilted – this is your <strong>saag sweet potato rice</strong></p>",
