      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>saag sweet potato rice</strong> and top with the<strong> mango paneer & courgette skewers </strong>and<strong> </strong>a dollop of<strong> coriander yoghurt</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
